STATE
v.
Claude Edward DAMMONS. No. 295P15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Nov. 19, 2015.

<page vol="778" reporter="S.E.2d" no="437" /> The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 17th of August 2015 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 19th of November 2015."
